Class NotificationData<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.NotificationData<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @PublicAPI
public class NotificationData<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    NotificationData is used by the Scheduler Core to notify the front-end of any changes. It is sent through notification methods in core interface.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9.1
